{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/autism-in-adults/diagnosis/when-to-suspect-autism/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"601a5c68-6301-5ae5-9fab-f5942d415fdd","slug":"when-to-suspect-autism","fullItemName":"When to suspect autism","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field c3b7f828-3914-41ed-af77-aa0600c8abe9 --><h2>When should I suspect possible autism spectrum disorder in an adult?</h2><!-- end field c3b7f828-3914-41ed-af77-aa0600c8abe9 -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item eb5a03f2-eef0-4d7b-8fb5-aa0600c8abe9 --><!-- begin field ff7506c6-f468-4f65-97f5-aa0600c8abe9 --><ul><li><strong>The identification, assessment, and diagnosis of autism spectrum disorder (ASD) in adults is challenging</strong> because ASD can coexist with a number of <a class=\"topic-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/autism-in-adults/background-information/definition/\">mental health disorders</a>, such as depression and schizophrenia. In addition, the <a class=\"topic-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/autism-in-adults/diagnosis/differential-diagnoses/\">differential diagnosis</a> from a range of other conditions can present difficulties.</li><li><strong>Consider assessment for possible ASD when a person has: </strong><ul><li>One or more of the following:<ul><li>Persistent difficulties in social interaction.</li><li>Persistent difficulties in social communication.</li><li>Stereotypic (rigid and repetitive) behaviours, resistance to change, or restricted interests, <em>and</em></li></ul></li><li>One or more of the following:<ul><li>Problems in obtaining or sustaining employment or education.</li><li>Difficulties in initiating or sustaining social relationships.</li><li>Previous or current contact with mental health or learning disability services.</li><li>A history of a neurodevelopmental condition (including learning disabilities and attention deficit hyperactivity disorder) or mental disorder.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><!-- end field ff7506c6-f468-4f65-97f5-aa0600c8abe9 --><!-- end item eb5a03f2-eef0-4d7b-8fb5-aa0600c8abe9 -->","topic":{"id":"32496f22-23a5-5fd3-af9d-aaa3ee19e8c4","topicId":"7875afe5-1be7-4d7d-aaee-aa0600c8a8b5","topicName":"Autism in adults","slug":"autism-in-adults","lastRevised":"Last revised in May 2020","chapters":[{"id":"1d801996-d965-5a13-8911-e1e73561bc33","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"9734a796-92be-5d8e-a449-165bb7c48303","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"923a675b-d678-557f-9c55-f812123295f0","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"c9e157b2-2b93-57bc-a59d-352858540bdf","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"44c0c065-104d-5b0e-910a-b79265e7660d","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"51bf61e4-2f0f-50af-9d9a-6e75814aa9db","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"01492dc4-77e0-59c1-b4fd-5770732d8d51","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"641ca12c-43c4-5274-ba37-b332755227a3","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"421104c4-9e4d-5105-a6f2-b13e16769a87","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"24fbca3b-5d6b-5f86-aa0d-f57e4aebb9a0","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"ef3c19b0-d066-5a2c-8de9-9f9173a490d6","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"b6cc75c0-bb75-5789-992d-d9e97d9ae77f","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"a653ef4b-e179-59b1-a4d6-7e87ea470c57","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"ed2e7d98-0e83-561f-be20-a925d3de34b2","slug":"definition","fullItemName":"Definition"},{"id":"da3472cb-1943-56b5-8882-6fcd83c3f90c","slug":"causes-risk-factors","fullItemName":"Causes and risk factors"},{"id":"f61a6e0e-dc1f-53b2-b699-99f4e31be15a","slug":"prevalence","fullItemName":"Prevalence"},{"id":"4b4ceddf-98c4-54d0-8a36-84313e59db55","slug":"complications","fullItemName":"Complications"},{"id":"344c3bb6-0377-5f99-be67-abb4ff28f0e8","slug":"prognosis","fullItemName":"Prognosis"}]},{"id":"210ffb54-6480-51ba-83c2-c866987feb52","fullItemName":"Diagnosis","slug":"diagnosis","subChapters":[{"id":"601a5c68-6301-5ae5-9fab-f5942d415fdd","slug":"when-to-suspect-autism","fullItemName":"When to suspect autism"},{"id":"5003a9ea-5b26-55b6-8155-06b4b7182728","slug":"differential-diagnoses","fullItemName":"Differential diagnoses"}]},{"id":"62fe3960-58ce-5083-9b58-a76b9683e18d","fullItemName":"Management","slug":"management","subChapters":[{"id":"cc01ebe2-f9cb-5033-b4d5-01e8b1fab61b","slug":"managing-suspected-autism","fullItemName":"Scenario: Managing suspected autism"},{"id":"ca091aca-f275-5bee-b969-85562c58af20","slug":"managing-confirmed-autism","fullItemName":"Scenario: Managing confirmed autism"}]},{"id":"298b625f-4f51-5d68-9fde-7208080172fc","fullItemName":"Supporting evidence","slug":"supporting-evidence","subChapters":[]},{"id":"bf82d908-c818-5e1d-95ac-11ae3717d59c","fullItemName":"How this topic was developed","slug":"how-this-topic-was-developed","subChapters":[{"id":"57e053b2-d553-5190-8f40-c19b0914a331","slug":"search-strategy","fullItemName":"Search strategy"},{"id":"3fc29edc-6452-5a4d-b428-e3f1f7d2b5c6","slug":"stakeholder-engagement","fullItemName":"Stakeholder engagement"},{"id":"fe358782-f480-51f1-8a8e-d097ad145d8e","slug":"evidence-exclusion-criteria","fullItemName":"Evidence exclusion criteria"},{"id":"40850acb-bfe1-5aba-a582-54233fa181b4","slug":"organizational-behavioural-financial-barriers","fullItemName":"Organizational, behavioural and financial barriers"},{"id":"534d3309-5d79-55c1-9507-d5d041bb89b5","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest"}]},{"id":"12e97033-8325-53ff-afdf-c4ea300441aa","fullItemName":"References","slug":"references","subChapters":[]}]},"parentChapter":{"id":"210ffb54-6480-51ba-83c2-c866987feb52","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},"subChapters":[{"id":"0494fa17-83f4-563f-9456-47a22a34abed","slug":"basis-for-recommendation-d3e","fullItemName":"Basis for recommendation","depth":3,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field d407e2fb-2c72-4362-9708-aa0600c8abe9 --><h3>Basis for recommendation</h3><!-- end field d407e2fb-2c72-4362-9708-aa0600c8abe9 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item d3ecf593-926f-4df8-9c85-aa0600c8abe9 --><!-- begin field 18dc9d17-989d-42ac-b128-aa0600c8abe9 --><p>These recommendations are based on the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) guidelines <em>Autism. Recognition, referral, diagnosis and management of adults on the autism spectrum</em> (full NICE guideline) [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/autism-in-adults/references/\">National Collaborating Centre for Mental Health, 2012</a>] and <em>Autism spectrum disorder in adults: diagnosis and management</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/autism-in-adults/references/\">NICE, 2016</a>]. For detailed information on the evidence NICE used to make these recommendations, see the <a data-hyperlink-id=\"d8d64040-72d8-4409-9be0-aa60015f17d7\" href=\"https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/cg142/evidence/full-guideline-pdf-186587677\">full NICE guideline</a>.</p><ul><li>The NICE guideline development group (GDG) used their expert knowledge and judgement, together with the diagnostic criteria and related information contained in existing diagnostic manuals (especially the Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders), to identify a number of signs and symptoms that were in their view likely to have sufficient sensitivity and specificity to improve the identification of autism spectrum disorder in adults and prompt assessment where necessary. </li><li>The GDG favoured sensitivity over specificity in this circumstance.</li></ul><!-- end field 18dc9d17-989d-42ac-b128-aa0600c8abe9 --><!-- end item d3ecf593-926f-4df8-9c85-aa0600c8abe9 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}